00:14:50.920 --> 00:14:52.000
Quando tudo acabar,

00:14:52.920 --> 00:14:53.960
Eu vou levar-te embora

00:14:55.640 --> 00:14:56.640
daqui,

00:14:57.320 --> 00:14:58.160
